modelDocumentation.formattedText:
Main Model 


This model displays the Overall Net profit by combining 3 different regions value. 


There are several product categories and product under each region.


P&L value of each product must be calculated, and this gets aggregated to region level. 


Template Structure  
Template Structure contains P&L Components as per desired hierarchy. 
Net Profit value is derived using Expense and Revenue as inputs. 
Product of Units Sold and Selling price along with Discount % is Sales value. 
Expense value is Sum of Cost of Sales and Other Costs. 
Node values which are derived from Data source i.e., Units Sold, Selling Price, Discount %, Cost of Sales etc will use the Type as Template Key. 
All the cost/expense related nodes have been configured with Decrease as Desired trend.
Additional Information


Template Structure is applied to leaf nodes i.e., Coffee, Orange, Cheese etc.
Clothing Product category is been configured with different template using the Template filter condition
